<item>
            <title>[FELIX-5738] EventAdmin IgnoreTopic config. property doesn&apos;t support wildcards</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-5738</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;EventAdminImpl is using package name matchers to implement IgnoreTopic, namely  PackageMatcher and SubPackageMatcher. These won&apos;t work when org.apache.felix.eventadmin.IgnoreTopic is set with a wildcard, such as org/osgi/service/log/*&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13115309">FELIX-5738</key>
            <summary>EventAdmin IgnoreTopic config. property doesn&apos;t support wildcards</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
